messages.messageBody:
Hello all,

Miyamoto Musashi wrote another book called "35 tactical lessons" that
he gave to his pupil TERAO Nobuyuki.

His main book "Go Rin No Sho" was sent to TERAO Katsunobu.

Someone knows if his book about Tactical lessons is available
somewhere?

Internet or libraries?

Thanks in advance,


Helly
